to be your first stop.

345
00:29:32,231 --> 00:29:35,166
Actually, I dropped
by Alison's first.

346
00:29:35,234 --> 00:29:36,895
Oh. And how is she?

347
00:29:39,705 --> 00:29:41,969
Not as honored.

348
00:29:42,040 --> 00:29:44,372
Don't worry, Will,
she'll come around.

349
00:29:44,443 --> 00:29:48,880
I missed you, Will. I never got to
thank you after all that went down.

350
00:29:48,947 --> 00:29:52,348
