00:29:59,091 --> 00:30:03,892
But you not ratting us out
really means something in my book.

354
00:30:03,962 --> 00:30:05,862
Like I said...

355
00:30:05,931 --> 00:30:07,523
You could've
ratted out Hoyt, though.

