for that guy.

358
00:30:12,971 --> 00:30:17,670
And I take it
you heard about Vince.

359
00:30:17,743 --> 00:30:19,005
Yes. That's terrible.

360
00:30:19,077 --> 00:30:21,272
I mean, he went really dark.

361
00:30:24,650 --> 00:30:26,743
