to hear about that.

388
00:31:59,044 --> 00:32:00,841
You listen to me, Gum.

389
00:32:00,913 --> 00:32:03,814
I have been waiting
eight years for this.

390
00:32:03,882 --> 00:32:05,543
Go ahead.

391
00:32:05,617 --> 00:32:07,847
I had to change my name,
erase everything.

392
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:10,616
