partner who ruined my life that night.

394
00:32:15,594 --> 00:32:17,960
Come on, man. Really?
We're gonna go back there?

395
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,327
You did that to yourself.

396
00:32:19,398 --> 00:32:21,958
Semantics.
I want my share.

397
00:32:22,034 --> 00:32:25,470
I want my share
of the $10 million

398
00:32:25,537 --> 00:32:28,165
<i>that was gonna</i>
<i>change our lives forever.</i>

399
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:30,174
