400
00:32:30,242 --> 00:32:36,977
[coughs] I had a feeling
you'd say that, Gum.

401
00:32:37,049 --> 00:32:39,483
I burned it just before
Harland got to me.

402
00:32:39,551 --> 00:32:42,384
No. Stop it.

403
00:32:42,454 --> 00:32:44,319
<i>It's true.</i>

