433
00:34:37,536 --> 00:34:42,405
Your father abandoned me
in my time of need...

434
00:34:42,474 --> 00:34:46,467
So I know what it is to be in the
position you're in. Really, I do.

435
00:34:46,545 --> 00:34:51,278
