981
01:27:53,862 --> 01:27:56,023
- Why?
- You're cooking again.

982
01:27:58,033 --> 01:28:00,092
Wake me up
if something happens.

983
01:28:18,787 --> 01:28:21,119
Don't you ever
clean your truck?

984
01:28:25,294 --> 01:28:28,525
Honey? Can you flip the
shrimp in three minutes?

985
01:28:28,597 --> 01:28:32,124
- Let go of the control, Dad. I got it.
- Letting go.

986
01:28:38,407 --> 01:28:41,205
Definitely more
than $300,000.

987
01:28:41,276 --> 01:28:44,211
And the house can use
a new roof, kitchen...

988
01:28:44,279 --> 01:28:47,009
He's got it. He's got that
missing ten pounds of gold.

989
01:28:47,082 --> 01:28:49,550
That's what they're talking
about, somethin' enough for ya?

990
01:28:49,618 --> 01:28:51,984
Yeah, that is something.

991
01:28:52,054 --> 01:28:56,013
- Well, if you fence that gold...
- Oh, I know. I know. They'll nail me.

992
01:28:56,091 --> 01:28:57,718
I can't see his lips.

993
01:28:57,793 --> 01:29:01,320
- I'm gonna disappear it in the mud.
- Okay.

994
01:29:03,665 --> 01:29:04,825
Here.

995
01:29:07,102 --> 01:29:09,900
<i>(Fletcher)</i>
<i>He's not gonna throw it.</i>

996
01:29:09,971 --> 01:29:12,269
He just might, and if he
does, you ain't got jack.

997
01:29:12,341 --> 01:29:14,741
- Don't throw it.
- Throw it.

998
01:29:14,810 --> 01:29:16,243
- <i>(Fletcher) Don't do it.</i>
- (Harland) <i>Do it.</i>

999
01:29:16,311 --> 01:29:18,176
- Throw it.
- Don't do it.

1000
01:29:18,246 --> 01:29:21,272
- Do it. Throw it. Throw it.
- Don't do it. No, no, no.

1001
01:29:21,350 --> 01:29:22,180
Do it.

1002
01:29:29,691 --> 01:29:32,455
Sure, yeah,
keep it, sell it.

1003
01:29:32,527 --> 01:29:34,586
Get rich.

1004
01:29:34,663 --> 01:29:36,028
And then
go back to jail.

1005
01:29:38,867 --> 01:29:41,859
Okay. All right.
It's going in.

1006
01:29:54,015 --> 01:29:56,779
Oh, thank you, Will.

1007
01:29:56,852 --> 01:29:58,683
I'll return to my life now.

